## ğŸ“ What Each Page Does

### Landing Page (`index.html`):
- Beautiful purple gradient design
- Shows features and pricing
- "Start Free Trial" button
- Gets people to sign up

### Login Page (`login.html`):
- Simple email/password login
- Routes to dashboard (users) or admin (you)

### Signup Page (`signup.html`):
- Name, email, password
- Automatically gives 30-day trial
- No credit card required
- Routes to dashboard after signup

### User Dashboard (`dashboard.html`):
- Shows their shortened URLs
- Click statistics
- Create new links
- Trial countdown
- Upgrade button

### Admin Dashboard (`admin.html`):
- **THIS IS YOUR CONTROL PANEL!**
- See everything happening in your business
- Track revenue
- Manage users
- Monitor growth

